LIEN IN USA

 MARTIN SORRY ABOUT DELAY REPLYING RE LIEN QUESTION

 WE WERE TRYING TO GET HOLD OF LONDON SHIPPING LAWYER FREIND WHO
GIVES AS FREE TELCON ADVICE

ANYWAY COULDN'T GET HIM OUT OF COURT

 SO MY OPINION IS THAT US LAW NOT VERY DIFF FROM UK LAW IN RESPECT OF
THE REQUIREMENT TO PROVE WHERE OWNERSHIP LIES.

 ITS VERY EASY TO GET A US JUDGE WHO DOES NOT KNOW SHIPPING TO ISSUE
A LIEN ON THE CARGO AS THEY DO NOT PROPERLY CHECK THE 'REAL'
OWNERSHIP.

 IN THE END DESPITE THE FACT THE THE COURT HAS ALLOWED THE LIEN YOU
SHOULD BE ABLE TO GET THE CARGO RELEASED PROVIDING YOU CAN PROVE THAT
YOU OWN THE PROPERTY AND NOVOKUZNETSK NO LONGER DOES.

 OVERAGED INSURANCE - I WILL LOOK THROUGH AND COMMENT

